=== 開發與製作背景 ===
2014年8月22日，[[CBS_(電視網)|CBS]]宣布簽署改編自萊恩·麥克蓋瑞（{{lang|en|Ryan McGarry}}）之同名紀錄片的醫療劇《黑色代碼》試播集協議，並由{{le|ABC工作室|ABC Studios}}製作、{{le|邁克爾·賽茲曼|Michael Seitzman}}執筆，而賽茲曼和麥克蓋瑞以及紀錄片製作人琳達·高德史坦·諾爾頓（{{lang|en|Linda Goldstein Knowlton}}）與{{le|瑪蒂·納克森|Marti Noxon}}將共同擔任執行製作。賽茲曼當初在觀賞紀錄片後，起了改編劇集的念頭，並在發現納克森為製作人之一後與其接洽，而納克森因執掌《{{le|閨蜜離婚指南|Girlfriends' Guide To Divorce}}》與《[[虛幻_(電視劇)|真實之虛]]》兩部劇集而身分乏術，因此賽茲曼幸運地全權掌舵本劇。劇名是取自[[醫院急救代碼|醫院急救代碼]]，而「黑色代碼」意指病患大量湧入醫院，但醫院卻沒有足夠的資源來治療病患，甚至可能有病患因此而死亡的情況。劇集和紀錄片的靈感，皆是來自一名年輕醫生加入[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]最繁忙卻專業的[[急診室|急診室]]團隊後，面臨如何在對抗殘破的體制下，堅持志向以及面對醫病關係的掙扎等。<ref name="Pilot">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2014/08/code-black-er-drama-from-michael-seitzman-cbs-put-pilot-commitment-823254/|title=ER Drama ‘Code Black’ From Michael Seitzman Gets CBS Put Pilot Commitment|publisher=Deadline.com|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|date=2014-08-22|accessdate=2017-10-31|archive-date=2021-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301233345/https://deadline.com/2014/08/code-black-er-drama-from-michael-seitzman-cbs-put-pilot-commitment-823254/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年1月27日，CBS預訂本劇試播集，並由{{le|ink-en|大衛·塞梅爾|David Semel}}執導身兼執行製作，而{{le|CBS電視工作室|CBS Television Studios}}也加入了製作行列。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/01/code-black-medical-drama-michael-seitzman-comedy-mike-gibbons-cbs-pilot-orders-1201360945/|title=‘Code Black’ Medical Drama From Michael Seitzman, Divorced-Dad Comedy Get CBS Pilot Orders|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|date=2015-01-27|accessdate=2016-01-23|publisher=Deadline|archive-date=2021-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214161319/https://deadline.com/2015/01/code-black-medical-drama-michael-seitzman-comedy-mike-gibbons-cbs-pilot-orders-1201360945/|dead-url=no}}</ref>6月4日，布雷特·馬霍尼（{{lang|en|Brett Mahoney}}）正式加入製作陣容，擔任執行製作。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/06/brett-mahoney-deal-cbs-studios-code-black-1201438019/|title=Brett Mahoney Inks CBS Studios Deal, Joins ‘Code Black’ As Executive Producer|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|date=2015-06-04|accessdate=2016-01-23|publisher=Deadline|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226055806/https://deadline.com/2015/06/brett-mahoney-deal-cbs-studios-code-black-1201438019/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年10月23日，CBS增訂了第1季6集劇本至19集。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/10/limitless-full-season-order-cbs-code-black-6-scripts-1201592506/|title='Limitless' Receives Full-Season Order From CBS, 'Code Black' Gets 6 Scripts|last=Nellie|first=Andreeva|work=Deadline.com|date=2015-10-23|accessdate=2015-10-23|archive-date=2015-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151024150215/http://deadline.com/2015/10/limitless-full-season-order-cbs-code-black-6-scripts-1201592506/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年11月20日，CBS宣布增訂第1季5集集數至18集。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2015/11/20/code-black-gets-5-more-episodes-from-cbs/|title='Code Black' gets 5 more episodes from CBS|last=Porter|first=Rick|work=TV by the Numbers|date=2015-11-20|accessdate=2015-11-20|archive-date=2015-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121184517/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2015/11/20/code-black-gets-5-more-episodes-from-cbs/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>2016年5月16日，CBS宣布續訂第2季。<ref name="CBS Renewals Season 2">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/05/code-black-criminal-minds-beyond-borders-odd-couple-undercover-boss-renewed-cbs-1201757112/|title=‘Code Black’, ‘Criminal Minds: Beyond Borders’, ‘The Odd Couple’ & ‘Undercover Boss’ Renewed By CBS|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|work=Deadline Hollywood|date=2016-05-16|accessdate=2016-05-16|archive-date=2016-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160517094212/https://deadline.com/2016/05/code-black-criminal-minds-beyond-borders-odd-couple-undercover-boss-renewed-cbs-1201757112/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2016年11月14日，宣布增訂第2季3集集數至16集。<ref name="Code, Great, Man">{{cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2016/11/cbs-orders-more-episodes-man-with-a-plan-the-great-indoors-code-black-1201853944/|title=CBS Orders More Episodes Of ‘Man With A Plan’, ‘The Great Indoors’ & ‘Code Black’|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|work=Deadline Hollywood|date=2016-11-14|accessdate=2016-11-14|archive-date=2016-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161114233634/http://deadline.com/2016/11/cbs-orders-more-episodes-man-with-a-plan-the-great-indoors-code-black-1201853944/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年5月14日，CBS宣布續訂第3季。<ref name="Season 3 Renewed">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/code-black-renewed-season-3-1003590|title=CBS's 'Code Black' Renewed for Third Season|last=Stanhope|first=Kate|last2=O'Connell|first2=Michael|work=[[荷里活報道|好萊塢報導]]|date=2017-05-14|accessdate=2017-05-14|archive-date=2017-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170516162947/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/code-black-renewed-season-3-1003590|dead-url=no}}</ref>2018年5月24日，賽茲曼於個人[[Twitter|Twitter]]上，宣布劇集遭到電視網取消的消息。<ref name="Cancelled">{{cite web|url=http://tvline.com/2018/05/24/code-black-cancelled-season-4-cbs/|title=''Code Black'' Cancelled at CBS|last=Gelman|first=Vlada|work=TVLine|date=2018-05-24|accessdate=2018-05-24|archive-date=2018-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180524153745/http://tvline.com/2018/05/24/code-black-cancelled-season-4-cbs/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

