s://deadline.com/2015/03/luis-guzman-cast-code-black-cody-horn-broad-squad-1201385562/|dead-url=no}}</ref>隔日，宣布[[拉薩·傑佛瑞|拉薩·傑佛瑞]]加入主演陣容，飾演堅守規則的優秀醫師尼爾，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/03/homeland-raza-jaffrey-cast-code-black-cbs-pilot-1201386066/|title=‘Homeland’s Raza Jaffrey To Co-Star In CBS Pilot ‘Code Black’|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|date=2015-03-04|accessdate=2016-01-23|publisher=Deadline|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211182600/https://deadline.com/2015/03/homeland-raza-jaffrey-cast-code-black-cbs-pilot-1201386066/|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[本·霍靈斯沃斯|班傑明·哈林斯沃思]]則飾演具野心又自大的新進住院醫師馬利歐。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/03/charity-wakefield-cast-female-lead-nbc-pilot-endgame-ben-hollingsworth-code-black-1201386913/|title=Charity Wakefield To Star In ‘Endgame’; Ben Hollingsworth Joins ‘Code Black’|last=Petski|first=Denise|date=2015-03-05|accessdate=2016-01-23|publisher=Deadline|archive-date=2021-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228142134/https://deadline.com/2015/03/charity-wakefield-cast-female-lead-nbc-pilot-endgame-ben-hollingsworth-code-black-1201386913/|dead-url=no}}</ref>3月9日，格蕾斯因「創作因素」，辭演了本劇。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvline.com/2015/03/09/maggie-grace-leaving-code-black-cbs-medical-drama-pilot/|title=Lost Vet Maggie Grace Exits CBS' Medical Drama Pilot Code Black|last=Ausiello|first=Michael|date=2015-03-09|accessdate=2016-01-23|publisher=TVLine|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125044018/https://tvline.com/2015/03/09/maggie-grace-leaving-code-black-cbs-medical-drama-pilot/|dead-url=no}}</ref>3月13日，在製作方考量哈登曾榮獲[[奧斯卡金像獎|奧斯卡金像獎]]的實力後，決定更改角色的年齡設定，由原定飾演克莉絲塔的哈登詮釋，並由[[邦妮·桑莫薇|邦妮·桑莫薇]]接演克莉絲塔一角。<ref name="Bonnie">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/03/marcia-gay-harden-star-code-black-pilot-bonnie-sommerville-recasting-cbs-1201392452/|title=Marcia Gay Harden Takes Over The Lead In ‘Code Black’, Bonnie Somerville Cast|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|date=2015-03-13|accessdate=2016-01-23|publisher=Deadline|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212011033/https://deadline.com/2015/03/marcia-gay-harden-star-code-black-pilot-bonnie-sommerville-recasting-cbs-1201392452/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

