e=2016-07-05|accessdate=2016-07-05|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227165444/https://tvline.com/2016/07/05/rob-lowe-code-black-season-2-cast-cbs/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

